{"tid":1849201,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"呢段時間坐飛機應該點應對好?","createTime":"2020-01-29T02:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:30:41.000Z","uid":9692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"332de7b479554636e4fb1c7e32e5a2b2a070a5be","tid":1849201,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"係唔係一定唔可以飲野同食野?<br />\n<br />\n全程戴口罩就一定啦"},{"pid":"0b924ae026c03ede400050bdfd9876f57f507058","tid":1849201,"uid":129739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"surgical mask都要隔幾個鐘頭換一次，唔係用耐左都係冇用。<br />\n短途機就可以戴住不吃不喝。長途你點都要除一除。"},{"pid":"a887919ec92777cc76a0861c1d073b50b4f6881a","tid":1849201,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b924ae026c03ede400050bdfd9876f57f507058","tid":1849201,"uid":129739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"surgical mask都要隔幾個鐘頭換一次，唔係用耐左都係冇用。<br />\n短途機就可以戴住不吃不喝。長途你點都要除一除。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"明白, 咁食野係唔係超高危? 如果真係要食應該點做?"},{"pid":"63f8e4d5a0e4acd83809dfe051ff0b64f81add14","tid":1849201,"uid":115888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"建議你自行消毒定個位，特別係張檯<br />\n因為飛機係唔會消毒每個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16305b5ec107906d86f507adbd76813fa8c2a0a2","tid":1849201,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"用酒精抹下個窗 張枱同遙控<br />\n唔好用航空公司既毛氈<br />\n應該仲有 不過未諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9101ae5acff4bb0469da946a3baaa87728d14e","tid":1849201,"uid":129739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a887919ec92777cc76a0861c1d073b50b4f6881a","tid":1849201,"uid":9692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b924ae026c03ede400050bdfd9876f57f507058","tid":1849201,"uid":129739,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:26:59.000Z","msg":"surgical mask都要隔幾個鐘頭換一次，唔係用耐左都係冇用。<br />\n短途機就可以戴住不吃不喝。長途你點都要除一除。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"明白, 咁食野係唔係超高危? 如果真係要食應該點做?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"照食囉，唔係點。<br />\n你上機前飲好晒水，食飽左。等4個鐘頭後有餐到，食野飲野，順便換埋個mask。<br />\n出入廁所都戴返個mask啦。但提一提個mask入面濕左都冇乜用，要換個，帶定幾個旁身。"},{"pid":"b675db22d5e0a493808163947dca7c4c777d37ad","tid":1849201,"uid":121358,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"見有人著雨嬲，用垃圾袋包住個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcbbae767decaadfda1da0bdfc17cf72af5ffc0","tid":1849201,"uid":71657,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"自己買㗎新飛機都唔係好貴"},{"pid":"1dd2ca782235b78afa628342b7ffceff758f0fa4","tid":1849201,"uid":25727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdcbbae767decaadfda1da0bdfc17cf72af5ffc0","tid":1849201,"uid":71657,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"自己買㗎新飛機都唔係好貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:08:52.000Z","msg":"飛機唔貴 養隊crew先無底深潭"},{"pid":"560104f4746feba436c93484ac8f08ea7a9dfdd9","tid":1849201,"uid":258877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:17:39.000Z","msg":"過兩日就飛 仲諗緊去唔去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3c57365c8789fe9c77bd991736b6236f30a571","tid":1849201,"uid":289140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:21:15.000Z","msg":"同問，推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bc184195fcdd2054852696f8fe7ddbaf1c5f45","tid":1849201,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=de3238f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=e4aa9247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=1c4d23f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=41d6e51b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=5ee17d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=dc3cdb5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=99a421fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fnpptl%2Ftopics%2Frespirators%2Ffactsheets%2Frespsars.html&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=80b4f156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/npptl/topics/respirators/factsheets/respsars.html</a><br />\nSARS 時期CDC 對N95 同防毒面具嘅指引<br />\n（僅供參考！WARS 嘅傳染性係SARS 嘅一倍以上！！！！）"},{"pid":"ccc4c326e0b4f7bd562beb1485cadc12e91eb8bc","tid":1849201,"uid":290260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"早兩日飛，機場所有人都戴口罩<br />\n最記得排隊買嘢，有個大陸人咳咗下，全條隊啲人散開哂，唔夠膽行近佢<br />\n<br />\n我上機即刻用濕紙巾消毒嗰位，全程戴口罩，食飯之前用消毒酒精洗手，每餐食完之後就換個新口罩，舊嗰個放落垃圾袋，封口<br />\n<br />\n嗰程機有個大陸細路仔不停咳，嚇死其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n如果短途機就建議唔好食飛機餐，減少除口罩嘅機會，我食飯之外，水都冇點飲，廢事除口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw如果去到外地見到有口罩賣，不防買定啲帶返香港，自用或者俾有需要嘅人都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住問清楚當地有冇限購令，一次唔好買好多盒，唔係嚇親當地人就唔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bcf044c8cc84c3ff8bdaaff24f74a7f6b5f1c5","tid":1849201,"uid":56921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"自己小心揀航空公司，睇下codeshare嘅航空公司有冇支那飛香港，睇下飛香港嘅機型有冇同時飛支那，避開篤航<br />\n<br />\n短途唔食野唔飲水<br />\n長途祝你好運<br />\n祝旅途愉快"},{"pid":"9139282d7ccc6ba33c17b489d61644db8d372e17","tid":1849201,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔好坐近廁所。可以既話唔好近走廊位。 拎消毒濕紙巾消毒座位"},{"pid":"6595b34e0a64f3a66065b1198aaeb126dcfea5f4","tid":1849201,"uid":233913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9139282d7ccc6ba33c17b489d61644db8d372e17","tid":1849201,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔好坐近廁所。可以既話唔好近走廊位。 拎消毒濕紙巾消毒座位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T20:10:03.000Z","msg":"有冇咩地方一定要抹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cee5fd0e60dd4beb193bd375e6d30c1996466e","tid":1849201,"uid":232304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6595b34e0a64f3a66065b1198aaeb126dcfea5f4","tid":1849201,"uid":233913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9139282d7ccc6ba33c17b489d61644db8d372e17","tid":1849201,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"唔好坐近廁所。可以既話唔好近走廊位。 拎消毒濕紙巾消毒座位"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T20:10:03.000Z","msg":"有冇咩地方一定要抹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"枱，安全帶扣，同櫈個手枕"}]}